         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="A Third-party order refers to a scenario where a company receives a customer order for a product or a service they do not deliver. In these instances, the company forwards the order to a third-party vendor who fulfills the order directly to the customer on behalf of the company. "/>
